---
// ABOUTME: Feature grid showcasing keytun's developer-focused qualities.
// ABOUTME: Six cards with keycap-styled icons, each with a distinct accent color.
---

<section class="section" id="features">
	<div class="container">
		<h2>Built for developers</h2>
		<div class="features-grid">
			<div class="feature" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-amber); --card-accent-rgb: 255, 186, 48;">
				<div class="keycap-small feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</div>
				<h3>Single binary</h3>
				<p>Go binary. No runtime, no dependencies. Download and run.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-peach); --card-accent-rgb: 255, 126, 82;">
				<div class="keycap-small feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔑</div>
				<h3>Readable session codes</h3>
				<p>Wordlist-based codes like <code>keen-fox-42</code>. Easy to say over a call.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature feature-highlight" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-mint); --card-accent-rgb: 77, 222, 122;">
				<div class="keycap-small feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔒</div>
				<div class="feature-title-row">
					<h3>End-to-end encrypted</h3>
					<span class="feature-badge">E2EE</span>
				</div>
				<p>X25519 key exchange + AES-256-GCM. The relay is a dumb pipe — it never sees your keystrokes or output.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-sky); --card-accent-rgb: 62, 201, 245;">
				<div class="keycap-small feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">☁️</div>
				<h3>Self-hostable relay</h3>
				<p>Stateless WebSocket broker. Deploy on Fly.io, Railway, or any container host.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-lavender); --card-accent-rgb: 176, 140, 255;">
				<div class="keycap-small feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌐</div>
				<h3>Browser client</h3>
				<p>Your colleague doesn't need to install anything. Share a link and they <a href="/join">join straight from the browser</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-coral); --card-accent-rgb: 255, 79, 56;">
				<div class="keycap-small feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">🪶</div>
				<h3>Lightweight</h3>
				<p>No database, no auth tokens, no persistence. Sessions live in memory.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(300px, 100%), 1fr));
		gap: 20px;
		margin-top: 48px;
	}

	.feature {
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		padding: 28px 24px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
	}

	/* Subtle top accent line */
	.feature::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 2px;
		background: var(--card-accent);
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.25s;
	}

	.feature:hover::before {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.feature:hover {
		border-color: rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.22);
		box-shadow:
			0 0 0 1px rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.06),
			0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28),
			0 0 32px rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.09);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	/* Highlighted card (encryption) */
	.feature-highlight {
		border-color: rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.15);
	}

	[data-theme="dark"] .feature-highlight {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.04));
	}

	.feature-title-row {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}

	.feature-title-row h3 {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.feature-badge {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.62rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--accent-mint);
		background: rgba(77, 222, 122, 0.08);
		border: 1px solid rgba(77, 222, 122, 0.2);
		padding: 2px 7px;
		border-radius: 4px;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	[data-theme="dark"] .feature-badge {
		background: rgba(77, 222, 122, 0.1);
		border-color: rgba(77, 222, 122, 0.25);
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(77, 222, 122, 0.15);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}

	/* Icon always tinted to card accent */
	.feature .keycap-small {
		background: rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.1);
		color: var(--card-accent);
	}

	.feature:hover .keycap-small {
		background: rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.18);
		box-shadow: var(--keycap-shadow-sm), 0 0 10px rgba(var(--card-accent-rgb), 0.2);
	}

	.feature h3 {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.feature p {
		color: var(--text-dim);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
